## Prerequisites
- Go 1.21+
- Docker (recommended)

## Environment
Create your env file:
```
cp .env.example .env
```

## Docker-first flow (recommended)
1) Start the database:
```
docker compose up -d db
```
2) Run migrations:
```
make migrate-up
```
3) Build and run the API:
```
docker compose up --build api
```

## Migrations
This template uses GORM AutoMigrate when enabled. If you prefer SQL migrations, the Makefile auto-installs the migrate CLI (first run requires internet):

Create a migration:
```
make migrate-create name=create_ping_logs
```

Run migrations:
```
make migrate-up
```

## Quick start (Go)
```
go run ./cmd/api
```

